民主黨立法會議員林卓廷表示，民主派議員均不同意「超時補水」，民主派會用盡一切方法阻止政府無限額地為警員加班費使用撥款。<br />\n<br />\n他批評，過去六個月，警隊涉及無數宗濫用暴力、職權及警黑勾結事件，嚴重侵害香港市民人權，如今反過來要求市民以公帑支付警隊「超時補水」，市民絕不接受。<br />\n<br />\n林卓廷表示，7.21事件警黑勾件，警察容讓大批黑社會長時間、無差別襲擊市民，但警方至今仍未找出事件主謀，警隊在過去半年的所作所為，國際社會及香港市民都看在眼內，政府理應重組警隊。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T07:28:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1497496-20191213.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1497496-20191213.htm&d=ZRuO0gn2PDb4CPS%2BM%2Fpj6koInKkgZqzseva8eQDkMF8%3D&h=f7f63ca4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1497496-20191213.htm&h=9a3a060f\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1497496-20191213.htm</a>"},{"pid":"caaeb902fb3916c717d155eb1718b803f0267a52","tid":1781220,"uid":94402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T07:31:21.000Z","msg":"除左拖撥款，仲要清算班狗<br />\n我要班狗有錢都無命享　<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nMON PO 狗，你地份糧染滿晒血架<br />\n你地食嘅狗糧，有血腥味架<br />\n你地繼續自己呃自己係正義囉，啲怨魂晚晚企係你地床邊望住你地"},{"pid":"c9494d793ea610518c21367e21f3df9af29e2525","tid":1781220,"uid":117607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T07:32:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f4b9718f077ce826bbede6e0158701a9b6cfa7b6","tid":1781220,"uid":267403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T07:37:12.000Z","msg":"我係公務員，我唔介意無得加人工！！攬炒吧！！！"},{"pid":"d4693545f685a7dbc292da4124c71b1ec4b0140c","tid":1781220,"uid":205180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T07:37:14.000Z","msg":"我想問，如果一陣四點，19賤波話唔洗搵曱甴強黎就可以繼續審，咁香港人點回應？"},{"pid":"cb0d4d0f62fa1571ecd78a61e0a758e0df0ac4eb","tid":1781220,"uid":97900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T07:39:15.000Z","ms